      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ANGELIC ANGEL (1) missed the frame latest (22.59) when fourth over 400m at Bulli in a Grade 4/5. Has two wins already from this draw. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. ZIPPING SNEAD (3) rocketed out of the boxes with a strong early sectional but gathered in and finished in the minors when third (29.89) at this track over 520m. Overdue and gets his chance. INTREPID EAGLE (5) has been in super consistent form, finishing in the minors at his last four runs. Last start finished 3rd over 516m at Dubbo beaten 11 lengths (30.00) behind Tank Keeping in a Grade 4/5 on February 7. Form from his last run is proving very strong. Overdue and is among the main hopes. THIRTEEN PLUS (2) was below best last time at Richmond (30.52) in a NG, finishing a 21 length eighth. Loves this draw, having won three of five starts.",
